***************************
Termius New October Edition
***************************

-------------------------------------------
=E2=9A=99=EF=B8=8F Restore your whole setup with Workspaces
-------------------------------------------

Workspaces can now save and restore your *entire working state* , including=
=C2=A0working path, running commands, and=C2=A0your *Local Terminal*. No mo=
re changing directories or restarting tools.

*How it works*

* Open your project folder, tail logs, run top, start vim=E2=80=94then save=
 it as a Workspace template.
* Next time, launch the workspace, and everything will come back exactly as=
 you saved it.

-----------------------------
=F0=9F=A4=96 Vibecoding on iOS, upgraded
-----------------------------

Hook up your favorite *CLI code agent* to a host in its settings. Termius w=
ill update the host icon for quick recognition and add a ready-to-run snipp=
et to start your agent instantly.

When connected, you can now *talk to your agent* right from the terminal. T=
he new input field makes prompts easy to edit and supports *speech-to-text*=
 , so you can literally ask your agent to handle tasks while you stay hands=
-on with the shell.

